Localization.Name: Klaus & Werner
Localization.Description: Formed in 2893, Klaus & Werner makes guns, and they make them well. This simple philosophy was the brainchild of Hector Klaus, a successful weapons inventor who believed above all else that simplicity of design would triumph in a combat situation.

Localization.Name: CF-117 Bulldog Repeater
Localization.Description:
Manufacturer: Klaus & Werner
Item Type: Laser Repeater
Size: 1

Featuring a three-barrel sequential fire design, the Klaus & Werner CF-117 Bulldog laser repeater is capable of delivering high velocity energy rounds while maintaining heat efficiency making it a favorite among new pilots who are outfitting their first ship.

Localization.Name: Banu
Localization.Description: Banu society combines the Human concepts of family and corporations into a single social unit know as a Souli, a cohabitation focused centered around a specific skillset. These Banu guilds do not control an entire market, rather there are always numerous Souli competing for the same market as the guilds are constantly in flux. \n\nBecause of this, the Banu do not market specific brand Soulis. Instead they simply market all their wares to Humans as Banu built.

English.Name: Banu

These Banu guilds do not control an entire market, rather there are always numerous Souli competing for the same market as the guilds are constantly in flux. \n\nBecause of this, the Banu do not market specific brand Soulis. Instead they simply market all their wares to Humans as Banu built.

Localization.Name: Argo ATLS IKTI Rad
Localization.Description:
Manufacturer: ASD
Focus: Combat
 
Taking an Argo ATLS modified for combat by the Banu merchant Wikelo, ASD has made further adjustments to the power suit so that it's better able to survive the deadly radiation storms on Pyro I.
